title: Microsoft Azure Virtual Machine: Disk
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check and the associated special agent (agent_azure) are deprecated
 and will be removed in a future version.

 Please configure the new special agent using the "Microsoft Azure" ruleset.

 This check provides information about VM disks in the Microsoft Azure cloud.
 The read and write throughput and the number of read and write operations
 are displayed.

 The thresholds can be configured using the rule "Azure VM Disk".

discovery:
 One service is created on every VM host. The option
 "Map data to the VM itself" has to be configured in the Azure agent.
